sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User as User (Mobile App)
    participant App as App Frontend
    participant IDV as Identity Verification<br/>(Jumio / Onfido / Socure)
    participant Screen as Screening Platform
    participant Risk as Risk Engine
    participant CBS as Core Banking System
    participant Analyst as KYC Analyst

    User->>App: Enter personal details<br/>(name, DOB, address, SSN)
    App->>IDV: Submit ID document image

    IDV->>IDV: OCR extraction<br/>Template matching<br/>Security feature check<br/>NFC chip read (if passport)
    IDV-->>App: Document verified

    App->>User: Take selfie video
    User->>App: Selfie captured
    App->>IDV: Submit selfie

    IDV->>IDV: Liveness detection<br/>(head turn, blink, 3D depth)<br/>Face match vs ID photo
    IDV-->>App: Biometric matched (98.5% confidence)

    App->>IDV: Request database verification
    IDV->>IDV: Cross-reference:<br/>Credit bureau, electoral roll,<br/>utility records, SSA
    IDV-->>App: Identity confirmed

    App->>Screen: Screen against lists
    Screen->>Screen: OFAC SDN<br/>EU / UN sanctions<br/>PEP databases<br/>Adverse media
    Screen-->>App: CLEAR (no hits)

    App->>Risk: Calculate risk score
    Risk->>Risk: Geography: low<br/>Product: standard<br/>PEP: no<br/>Industry: salaried<br/>Score: LOW
    Risk-->>App: Risk = LOW

    alt Low risk - auto-approve
        App->>CBS: Create account
        CBS-->>App: Account number assigned
        App-->>User: Account opened!<br/>< 5 minutes total
    end

    alt High risk or screening hit
        App->>Analyst: Refer for manual review
        Analyst->>Analyst: EDD investigation<br/>Source of wealth<br/>Additional documentation
        Analyst-->>App: Approved / Declined
    end

    Note over User,CBS: STP rate target: 70-90%<br/>for low-risk retail customers
